*rarian-0.8.0 (23 Mar 2008)

  23 Mar 2008; Mart Raudsepp <leio@gentoo.org> +rarian-0.8.0.ebuild:
  New version for GNOME-2.22. Recognizes lzma packed man and info pages,
  follows new freedesktop specification for categorization which causes it to
  not work well with yelp-2.20 - use a matching yelp-2.22

